                  "answerKey": "answer_1",
                  "content": "In order to answer questions about human behavior, we need to move beyond guesswork and common sense."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "The only way for sociological problems to be solved is through research."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
                  "content": "It will lead to understanding what will solve and eliminate the problem."
                },
